webpackJsonp([39244539979680],{1052:function(t,e){t.exports={data:{wordpressPost:{title:"The Best Gear For Your Next Workout (Blast Fat And Look Good Too)",content:'<p>We&#8217;re well across the fact that exercise is good for us.</p>\n<p>And if we were super keen we&#8217;d list all the physical and mental benefits of working up a sweat three to five (or more) times a week right here &#8211; but like we said &#8230; We&#8217;re well across this and we know you are too!</p>\n<p>What you might not know about is the following SEVEN truly excellent items. We swear they will make exercise fun, or easier at least &#8211; or, just tolerable, and definitely more stylish. And that&#8217;s a good thing!</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2715 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215032/PE-Nation-JPG-157x300.jpg" alt="" width="157" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215032/PE-Nation-JPG-157x300.jpg 157w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215032/PE-Nation-JPG.jpg 395w" sizes="(max-width: 157px) 100vw, 157px" />\n<p><a href="http://www.stylerunner.com/P.E-Nation-The-Countback-Tank-17PE3I062">P.E Nation The Countback Cropped Tank, $99.</a></p>\n<p>Cool, breezy, comfortable. You can work out in this all day long and then hit the dance floor. Yes! Well, maybe. You know what we mean though right? It&#8217;s versatile.</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2711 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22212409/S25-17272-Nimble-LAUREN-78-TIGHTS-JungleLeaf-087-200x300.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22212409/S25-17272-Nimble-LAUREN-78-TIGHTS-JungleLeaf-087-200x300.jpg 200w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22212409/S25-17272-Nimble-LAUREN-78-TIGHTS-JungleLeaf-087-768x1152.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22212409/S25-17272-Nimble-LAUREN-78-TIGHTS-JungleLeaf-087-683x1024.jpg 683w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22212409/S25-17272-Nimble-LAUREN-78-TIGHTS-JungleLeaf-087.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" />\n<p><a href="https://nimbleactivewear.com/products/lauren-7-8-tights-jungle-leaf">Nimble Lauren 7/8 Tights In Jungle Leaf, $95</a>.</p>\n<p>These tights are cute as a button. Plus, they suck you in in all the right places and give you that long, lean look we all covet so much. Good for strolling, running and sipping lattes &#8211; that&#8217;s exercise right?</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2717 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215115/The-Upside-JPG-229x300.jpg" alt="" width="229" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215115/The-Upside-JPG-229x300.jpg 229w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215115/The-Upside-JPG.jpg 373w" sizes="(max-width: 229px) 100vw, 229px" />\n<p><a href="https://www.theupsidesport.com/catalog/product/view/id/12865/s/rainbow-brights-andie-crop-indigo-upl1341/category/4/">The Upside Rainbow Brights Andie Crop, $109.</a></p>\n<p>A sweet yet sexy and most importantly, comfortable, sports bra that comes with matching tights too. We love this ensemble for beach walks and casual strolling. Sunscreen please!</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2720 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215352/Bag-JPG-246x300.jpg" alt="" width="246" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215352/Bag-JPG-246x300.jpg 246w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215352/Bag-JPG.jpg 396w" sizes="(max-width: 246px) 100vw, 246px" />\n<p><a href="http://www.lululemon.com.au/p/women-bags/Enroute-Bag/_/prod7190080?rcnt=48&amp;N=7rr&amp;cnt=222&amp;color=LW9AGJS_026624">Lululemon Enroute Bag II, $129.</a></p>\n<p>This slouchy bag is everything. It fits all you need plus looks chic and, is easy to toss on and carry everywhere you go. No kids &#8211; I will not carry your video games in here! Wait, did I say that out loud?</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2718 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215157/LJ-JPG-221x300.jpg" alt="" width="221" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215157/LJ-JPG-221x300.jpg 221w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215157/LJ-JPG.jpg 418w" sizes="(max-width: 221px) 100vw, 221px" />\n<p><a href="https://www.lornajane.com.au/-collection/-tops/lj-everyday-sweat/p-041722_CANM_S">Lorna Jane Everyday Sweat, $89.99.</a></p>\n<p>Look, some days aren&#8217;t people days &#8211; plain and simple. But you still got to get out and make it happen. Wear this chic sweatshirt and let the world know &#8211; I&#8217;m having a little me time folks. You feel me?</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2721 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215432/JPG-Nike-Air-Zoom-Pegasus-34-Womens-Running-Shoe-180-300x176.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="176" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215432/JPG-Nike-Air-Zoom-Pegasus-34-Womens-Running-Shoe-180-300x176.jpg 300w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215432/JPG-Nike-Air-Zoom-Pegasus-34-Womens-Running-Shoe-180.jpg 603w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />\n<p><a href="https://store.nike.com/au/en_gb/pd/air-zoom-pegasus-34-running-shoe/pid-11382132/pgid-11674426">Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 34 Women&#8217;s Running Shoe, $180.</a></p>\n<p>As a long-time runner, I swear by these shoes. They&#8217;re light and comfortable with just the right amount of bounce. And if you don&#8217;t run, they make you look like you do. I consider that almost as good as the real deal. Almost.</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2719 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215250/RB-JPG-169x300.jpg" alt="" width="169" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215250/RB-JPG-169x300.jpg 169w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22215250/RB-JPG.jpg 331w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" />\n<p><a href="https://www.runningbare.com.au/the-new-guard-muscle-tank/black2">Running Bare The New Guard Muscle Tank, $49.99.</a></p>\n<p>Look, some days the idea of a sweat session just does not appeal. Pure and simple. It can feel like nothing more than one more thing you have to do. But that&#8217;s the truth of the matter &#8211; it is something you have to do. So get out there and do it. This tank will help. Looks ace too &#8211; and that always helps.</p>\n<p><strong>And while we&#8217;ve got you &#8230;</strong></p>\n<figure id="attachment_2709" style="width: 300px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-medium wp-image-2709" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22211056/BB-Sisters-JPG-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22211056/BB-Sisters-JPG-300x300.jpg 300w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22211056/BB-Sisters-JPG-150x150.jpg 150w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/22211056/BB-Sisters-JPG.jpg 592w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Image: Instagram/@basebodybabes</figcaption></figure>\n<p>These two hotties are the <a href="http://www.basebodybabes.com/#">Base Body Babes</a> &#8211; and babes they are too. A little more detail (because you need that) &#8230; the babes are made up of sisters <strong>Diana Johnson</strong> and <strong>Felicia Oreb</strong> (above), both personal trainers with impressive creds. Plus, they&#8217;re all about inspiring women to be happy, healthy, fit and strong &#8211; and we love that.</p>\n<p>They offer training programs and nutritional ones too and heck, all the good fitness stuff. They are NOT about looking good (although they do and if you work with them, you will too) but feeling fit and strong and liking what you see in the mirror. And we love that attitude.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;d like to learn more about these dynamic duo and the services they offer, you can do exactly that <a href="http://www.basebodybabes.com">right here</a>. And if they help you to get your life on track (and they bloody can &#8211; swear it) let us know. We love a transformation story!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n',better_featured_image:{source_url:"http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/23121815/Base-Body-Babes-JPG.jpg"},categories:[{slug:"lifestyle",name:"Lifestyle"}]},site:{siteMetadata:{title:"The Beauty Insider"}}},pathContext:{id:"95055c28-f7e3-5370-8e69-72c3b7a65a5b"}}}});
